" employee enters a time of 5.5 hours on a timesheet, and "
":guilabel:`Rounding` is set to :guilabel:`No Rounding`, the entry remains "
"5.5 hours. If :guilabel:`Rounding` is set to :guilabel:`Half Day`, the entry"
